text.headline: The first computer to win a chess game against a world champion
text.text: The first match between Garry Kasparov and Deep Blue took place in February 1996. Deep Blue won the first game, but Kasparov won the overall match.

text.headline: Jeopardy! Victory
text.text: IBM's Watson competed on Jeopardy! and won against two of the show's greatest champions

text.headline: GPT-3 is introduced by OpenAI in June 2020
text.text: GPT-3 is one of the largest language models ever created, with 175 billion parameters
